description: Watch 22 year-old latino hardbody Jorge in a sultry solo! If you've visited sunny Puerto Rico, and spent time relaxing on the beautiful white sand beaches east of San Juan, you've probably gazed upon the tanned likes of Jorge. Working as a lifeguard keeps this handsome 22 year old latin boy beautifully tanned, but it's what he works on after the beaches close for the night that keeps him in such exquisite physical shape! In addition to the exotic San Juan party and club scene, Jorge enjoys running and scuba diving. At a compact 5'8' tall and 150 lbs. of solid muscle (not to mention a generous 7' love muscle), Jorge is one ultra-popular stud about town!
title: CitiBoyz 6: Frat Boy Sean & Friends, Scene #07
